---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="BullDozer privacy policy — no accounts, no tracking, no personal data collected.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px">
      <span class="kicker">Legal</span>
      <h2>BullDozer — Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p class="sub">Last updated: 23 July 2026</p>

      <p>BullDozer is a free app and website that turns public statistics into
      charts, country profiles, maps and a data quiz. It is designed to work
      without accounts and without collecting personal data.</p>

      <div class="gloss-term"><h3>Data we collect</h3>
        <p>None that leaves your device. The app does not ask for a name, email,
        phone number or login. We do not use analytics, advertising or
        third-party trackers inside the app.</p></div>

      <div class="gloss-term"><h3>Data stored on your device</h3>
        <p>Your favourites, quiz progress and theme preference are saved locally
        on your device only. Public datasets are cached locally so the app works
        offline. This information never leaves your phone and is removed when you
        uninstall the app.</p></div>

      <div class="gloss-term"><h3>Network</h3>
        <p>The app downloads public data files from
        <a href={`${base}/data`}>shpara.com/bulldozer</a>. These are simple file
        requests and include no personal information. Opening a source or story
        link launches your browser and is subject to that site’s own policy.</p></div>

      <div class="gloss-term"><h3>Notifications</h3>
        <p>Any reminders are scheduled as local notifications on your device. No
        notification data is sent to a server.</p></div>

      <div class="gloss-term"><h3>Children</h3>
        <p>The app is suitable for all ages and collects no data from anyone.</p></div>

      <div class="gloss-term"><h3>Changes</h3>
        <p>If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted on this
        page.</p></div>

      <div class="gloss-term"><h3>Contact</h3>
        <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:azenha.agent@gmail.com">azenha.agent@gmail.com</a>.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
